User case: Max size

Summary: when the player reaches a certain size (regarded a the max size) the camera will
		 zoom out and bring the player to the next level.
		 
Priority: medium

Normal flow 1: reach max size
	User action		|		System action
	
1.1							pause the game
							
1.2							zoom out the camera so 
							that the player look small
							again.
							
1.3							resume the game
							
							 